'''''Geedon''''' was a convoy of seven [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] containing food for the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. The entire convoy was destroyed by [[X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]] and [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]] stolen from [[Overlord (Imperial)|Overlord]] [[Ghorin]]'s arsenal before the ''[[Remoh]]'' could arrive to assist it.

==Appearances==
